dcterms:creator: E. Turcan
K. McKeown
dcterms:description: The Dreaddit dataset consists of lengthy posts in five different categories and is used for classifying stressful posts from casual conversations. It contains manually labeled posts categorized into stressful and non-stressful conversations.
dcterms:title: Dreaddit

dcterms:creator: A. Haque
V. Reddi
T. Giallanza
dcterms:description: The SDCNL dataset is scraped from Reddit social media platform from two subreddits: r/SuicideWatch and r/Depression. It is manually labeled to classify posts related to clinical depression and suicidal tendencies.
dcterms:title: SDCNL
